text: Tang Chia-hung (born 23 September 1996) is a Taiwanese artistic gymnast. In 2018, he won the gold medal in the horizontal bar and the silver medal in the floor exercise at the 2018 Asian Games held in Jakarta, Indonesia. In 2017, he finished in 4th place in the men's floor event at the 2017 Summer Universiade held in Taipei, Taiwan. At the 2019 Summer Universiade in Naples, Italy, he won the gold medal in the horizontal bar event.
